    "description": "<strong>Grapple Bot</strong> is a short, challenging platformer where you struggle to jump and grapple your way to the very top.<br><br>Traverse a variety of environments with unique features that will either aid you or be a detriment to your climb to the top of one big map.<br><br><strong><u>Junkyard Caverns</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/fa50e5b8fecb0d0c30cd88cc95559f81.poster.avif?t=1725360775\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/fa50e5b8fecb0d0c30cd88cc95559f81.webm?t=1725360775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/fa50e5b8fecb0d0c30cd88cc95559f81.mp4?t=1725360775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>The Ancient Ruins</u></strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/a105a0ca7fc2c251ee224b508d6ccf37.poster.avif?t=1725360775\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/a105a0ca7fc2c251ee224b508d6ccf37.webm?t=1725360775\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161420/extras/a105a0ca7fc2c251ee224b508d6ccf37.mp4?t=1725360775\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><u>How to play</u></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Move with keys 'A' and 'D', pressing 'SPACE' to jump.<br></li><li>Aim with your mouse cursor, hold left click and release to shoot your grapple hand to pull yourself towards the target. The length of your grappling hook depends how long you hold.<br></li><li>Press 'SPACE' to release using the momentum of the grapple to reach greater heights.</li></ul><br>You have only one save and it only saves when you exit the game, so play carefully otherwise your progress might disappear. There is a timer to track how long you have taken so compare with friends and compete for the fastest time.<br><br>A comfy sunchair is waiting for you at the very top, good luck...",
